<li id="cite_note-47"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-47">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5grD8OzyluD-e45ZwZb4rrURyZF-A">"Opposition supporters riot over priest's arrest"</a>, AFP, 13 November 2008.</span></li>
